feedback_text: The product works well but the pricing tiers are confusing. I had to contact support three times just to understand what I was paying for.
Absolutely love it! The onboarding was smooth and intuitive. Wish there were more integrations though.
Too expensive for what you get. Competitors offer similar features at half the price. Considering switching.
Decent product but support response times are slow. Waited 48 hours for a simple question.
Good value overall. The learning curve was steeper than expected but worth it once you get the hang of it.
Terrible experience. The app crashed during my demo to stakeholders. Completely unacceptable.
Best tool in its category. The recent updates have been fantastic. Keep up the great work!
The mobile app needs serious work. Features that work on desktop don't exist on mobile.
Solid product. Would appreciate more customization options for reports and dashboards.
Onboarding was confusing. The documentation is outdated and doesn't match the current UI.
Exceeded expectations. Implementation was quick and the ROI was visible within weeks.
Support team is amazing but the product itself has too many bugs. Fix the basics first.
Reliable and consistent. No major complaints but also no wow factor. Does what it says.
The interface is cluttered and overwhelming. Took me weeks to figure out basic workflows.
Easy to use but feature-limited compared to what was promised in the sales pitch.
Game changer for our team. The automation features alone save us 10 hours per week.
Average product. Nothing special but gets the job done. Wish pricing was more transparent.
Constant downtime. We've had three outages this month. How is this acceptable?
Great product with room for improvement. The roadmap looks promising.
Good support but the product doesn't deliver on its promises. Feels half-baked.
Exactly what we needed. Integration with our existing tools was seamless.
Works fine but overpriced. The team plan pricing doesn't make sense for small teams.
Solid choice. Minor UX issues but overall a good experience.
Documentation is lacking. Had to figure out most things through trial and error.
Perfect fit for our use case. The customer success team went above and beyond.
Product is okay but support is unresponsive. Still waiting on a ticket from two weeks ago.
Happy customer. Minor bugs occasionally but nothing deal-breaking.
Worst purchase decision we made. Complete waste of budget. Do not recommend.
Support is excellent. They helped us customize the solution to our exact needs.
Outstanding! This tool has transformed how our team operates. Worth every penny.
Good tool but the pricing model needs rethinking. Per-seat pricing doesn't scale well.
Steep learning curve and poor documentation combo is frustrating. Need better tutorials.
Reliable platform. Would recommend to others in our industry.
Good value but support SLAs are not being met. Response times are too long.
Excellent product. The recent feature additions have addressed most of our concerns.
Pricing increased 40% this year with no new features. Feeling nickel-and-dimed.
User-friendly and well-designed. Onboarding new team members is a breeze.
Middle of the road. Does what it needs to but nothing exceptional.
Would recommend. Has improved significantly since we first started using it.
Multiple critical bugs in production. Lost data twice. Actively looking for alternatives.
Best investment our team has made. The productivity gains are measurable.
Interface could be cleaner. Too many clicks to accomplish simple tasks.
Good product, fair price. Wish the mobile app had feature parity with desktop.
Promised features have been 'coming soon' for over a year now. Losing trust.
Solid experience overall. Support team is particularly helpful and knowledgeable.
Exceeded our expectations. Will be renewing for another year.
Adequate for our needs. Nothing more, nothing less.
Too many workarounds required for basic functionality. Needs polish.
Generally satisfied. The recent usability improvements are appreciated.
Fantastic tool. Our entire team is more efficient because of it.
